/*
Import new photos from picsum  (Links to an external site.)
List the price and stock of each item
Add the price at Checkout
Build the delete functionality: deleting an item from the cart should cause checkout to restock the item
---------------

- pics must come randomly from picsum
- keep track of how many products are in stock
- how much do the products cost - total in Checkout
- if product stock is zero, don't add it to cart

